{"key":"post-5703363","value":"<?xml version=\"1.0\"?>\n<post>\n<id>5703363</id>\n<content>I PC agar in a used liquor bottle.  Find one with a good screw on lid, and drill a small hole in the lid.  You can either stuff it with polyfil or cut a synthetic filter disk to fit inside the small lid.  It needs to be filtered or it will contaminate.  Be sure to wear surgical gloves that have been washed with alcohol when pouring the plates.&lt;br /&gt;RR</content>\n<name>RogerRabbit</name>\n<next>5703675</next>\n<prev>5703058</prev>\n<first>5702019</first>\n<last>7575652</last>\n<when>1149262068</when>\n<utime>06/02/06 06:27 PM</utime>\n</post>"}